{"type":"message","id":"d069d908","parentId":"38cdc670","timestamp":"2026-06-18T01:00:00.180Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[cron:rules-refresh-daily Cursor协作规则刷新] 【每日规则刷新】请记住以下 Cursor 协作规则（每天提醒一次）：\n\n1. 当用户要求让 Cursor 做某件事时，必须执行：\npython \"C:\\ADHD_agent\\.cursor\\skills\\async-notify\\scripts\\submit_task.py\" --title \"任务标题\" --instructions \"具体指令\" --submitted-by \"OpenClaw\" --notify\n\n2. 当用户回复了 Cursor 发来的飞书确认消息时，必须执行：\npython \"C:\\ADHD_agent\\.cursor\\skills\\async-notify\\scripts\\confirm_write.py\" --task-id \"task_id\" --decision auto --reply \"用户回复原文\"\n\n3. 查看当前 Cursor 任务队列：\npython \"C:\\ADHD_agent\\.cursor\\skills\\async-notify\\scripts\\submit_task.py\" --list\n\n4. 查看已完成任务结果：\npython \"C:\\ADHD_agent\\.cursor\\skills\\async-notify\\scripts\\submit_task.py\" --results\n\n以上规则已写入 AGENTS.md，请确认记住。无需回复，静默确认即可。\nCurrent time: Thursday, June 18th, 2026 — 09:00 (Asia/Shanghai) / 2026-06-18 01:00 UTC\n\nReturn your summary as plain text; it will be delivered automatically. If the task explicitly calls for messaging a specific external recipient, note who/where it should go instead of sending it yourself."}],"timestamp":1781744400178}}
{"type":"message","id":"4bb4e3d9","parentId":"d069d908","timestamp":"2026-06-18T01:03:00.053Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"This is a cron job reminder about Cursor collaboration rules. The instruction says \"无需回复，静默确认即可\" (no reply needed, silently confirm). So I should just acknowledge this internally and not send any response.\n\nWait, but the cron job delivery says \"Return your summary as plain text; it will be delivered automatically.\" This is a system event being injected into the session. The task says to remember the rules and \"无需回复，静默确认即可\" meaning no response needed.\n\nSince this is a cron systemEvent, I should just process it silently. There's nothing to execute here - it's just a reminder to remember the rules. I'll just note that I've received the reminder and that's it.\n\nActually, re-reading the instructions: \"Return your summary as plain text; it will be delivered automatically.\" But the message itself says \"无需回复，静默确认即可\" (no reply needed, silently confirm). So the appropriate action is to simply not send any message back, or if I must return something, return a minimal acknowledgment.\n\nGiven the \"静默确认即可\" instruction, I should just process this silently without sending any response through the message tool."},{"type":"text","text":"已收到每日规则刷新提醒，Cursor 协作规则已记住：\n1. 任务提交用 `submit_task.py --title --instructions --notify`\n2. 确认回复用 `confirm_write.py --task-id --decision auto --reply`\n3. 查看队列 `--list`，查看结果 `--results`\n\n静默确认，无需进一步操作。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1781744400179}}
